quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"Declare: “I seek refuge with Rabb of the day-break"
  113,2,against the evil-effect of that which He has created
  113,3,and against the evil-effect of darkness when it has fully set
  113,4,and against the evil-effect of those personalities who try to create sabotage in a commitment
  113,5,and against the evil-effect of an envious when he envied.”